### Password Operations Testing
### Test password change, reset, and security features

# Variables (Update after login)
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7249@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@adminEmail = admin@bantayvang.vn

### 1. Test Change Password - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "admin123",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### 2. Test Change Password - Wrong Current Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "wrong_password",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### 3. Test Change Password - Weak New Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "admin123",
  "newPassword": "123",
  "confirmPassword": "123"
}

### 4. Test Change Password - Password Mismatch
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "admin123",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "DifferentPassword123!"
}

### 5. Test Request Password Reset
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/request-reset
Content-Type: application/json

"{{adminEmail}}"

### 6. Test Request Password Reset - Non-existent Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/request-reset
Content-Type: application/json

"nonexistent@email.com"

### 7. Test Reset Password (Need to get token from logs/email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "RESET_TOKEN_FROM_LOGS",
  "newPassword": "ResetPassword123!"
}

### 8. Test Reset Password - Invalid Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "invalid_reset_token",
  "newPassword": "ResetPassword123!"
}

### 9. Test Change Password Without Authentication (Should Fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "admin123",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}